<plot>It's a coming-of-middle age movie of four high school girlfriends getting together for a long overdue, one night, reunion. After initial lies about their present lives, they each come to realize their own bitterness, dissatisfaction and disillusionment-wondering how they got to the places they are now. As the night comes to a close, they settle their differences over the contents of the hotel mini bar and it becomes clear that they each have a decision to make- a crossroads in their lives.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?017321</url></doc>
